    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bark cloth of Hawaii and other Polynesian Islands, made by pounding the bark of the paper mulberry, breadfruit, or other plants.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
